## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives or the latest developments in the field. The search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude relevant insights from non-English speaking regions. Additionally, the dynamic nature of IT means that ethical, legal, and social issues are continually evolving, and ongoing research is necessary to stay updated.

